Peter Thiel

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Peter Thiel



Thiel speaking in Berlin, March 2014



Born
Peter Andreas Thiel
(1967-10-11) October 11, 1967 (age 49)
Frankfurt, West Germany
(now Germany)


Citizenship
Germany
United States
New Zealand


