 Peter Thiel
(II)


 
Producer





Peter Thiel was born on October 11, 1967 in Frankfurt am Main, Hesse, Germany. He is a producer, known for Thank You for Smoking (2005), Ivory Tower (2014) and 60 Minutes (1968).            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

October 11, 
     
1967

            in
            Frankfurt am Main, Hesse, Germany











 


